    "Separate sessions of ChatGPT (GPT-4) were used for prompt #1 and prompt #2.",
    "DDIs were classified as highly clinically relevant if they required an immediate actionable intervention (e.g., dose or therapy change).",
    "Patient harm occurring from an incorrect or incomplete DDI recommendation was defined as an adverse health outcome that was likely to occur directly resulting from the mismanaged DDI.",
